-if @queue.count == 0
	%h1 You need more potatoes!
	%br
	Make sure to take a closer look at some potatoes if you want to add them to your queue.
- else
	%h1 The current potatoes in your lineup:
	%br
	.row
		- @queue.each do |movie, poster|
			.span2
				%h4
					#{movie.title}
	.row
		- @queue.each do |movie, poster|
			.span2
				.movie-poster
					%a{ :href => removequeue_path(:toremove => movie) }
						%img{ :src => "#{poster}", :onerror => "this.src='/assets/defaultposter.png'" }
	%br
	Click on potato poster to remove potato from your queue. Otherwise click <a href="/me/removequeue?toremove=empty">here</a> to empty your queue.

- if Rails.env.development?
	%br
	%br
	%h3 Queue: #{current_user.queue}